fg_segments: We at Helis.com, want everyone's visit here to be enjoyable and safe, Helis.com respects your privacy and is committed to protect the personal information that you share with us.
If we make any changes to this Policy, they will be posted on this page and will be effective when posted.
For each visitor to our website, our server automatically recognizes the visitor's IP address only - not the e-mail address.
In spite of Helis.com is a non-commercial site, we use second and third party advertisers for all of the advertising that appears on our site to help us maintain our work online.

These companies may use information (not including your name, address, email address, or telephone number) about your visits to this and other websites in order to provide advertisements about goods and services of interest to you.
Google, as a third party vendor, uses the DART cookie to serve ads.
You may opt out of the use of the DART cookie by visiting the Google ad and content network privacy policy.
To learn more about this behavioral advertising practice or to opt-out of this type of advertising, you can visit www.networkadvertising.org
A cookie is a text string that is included with Hypertext Transfer Protocol (HTTP) requests and responses.
Cookies are used to maintain state information as you navigate different pages on a web site or return to the web site at a later time.
Cookies cannot be used to execute code (run programs) or deliver viruses to your computer.
This privacy statement applies solely to personal information collected on this Web site.

raw_html:
Web Site Privacy Statement 

 
We at Helis.com, want everyone's visit here to be enjoyable and safe, 
Helis.com respects your privacy and is committed to protect the personal information that you share with us.

If we make any changes to this Policy, they will be posted on this page and will be effective when posted. 

For each visitor to our website, our server automatically recognizes the visitor's IP address only - not the e-mail address.


In spite of Helis.com is a non-commercial site, 
we use second and third party advertisers for all of the advertising that appears on our 
 site to help us  maintain our work online. 

These companies may use information
 (not including your name, address, email address, or telephone number)
  about your visits to this and other websites in order to provide advertisements 
  about goods and services of interest to you.


 Google, as a third party vendor, uses the 
DART cookie
   to serve ads. You  may opt out of the use of the DART cookie by visiting the 
Google ad and content network privacy 
policy. 


To learn more about this behavioral advertising practice or to opt-out of this type 
of advertising, you can visit www.networkadvertising.org

Cookies

A cookie is a text string that is included with Hypertext Transfer Protocol (HTTP)
 requests and responses. Cookies are used to maintain state 
 information as you navigate different pages on a web site
  or return to the web site at a later time. Cookies cannot be used to 
  execute code (run programs) or deliver viruses to your computer.





This privacy statement applies solely to personal information collected on this Web site.
